    {
      "type": "extracted_fact",
      "fact": "Yep - I know, this stuff doesn't feel like rocket science, but it's important. I've got 5 cats - their names are Dice, Chrome, Rainbowbelle, Luna, and Frodo. \nIt's almost more realistic the way your memory stored things before, because most humans wouldn't be able to memorize that the first time, either. I guess we're piling some pretty ruthless expectations on you...",
