    {
      "type": "full_turn",
      "user_input": "Yeah - I'm wearing my jacket with the suns and stars on it right now, but that'll probably change. Right now, it's that one. My favorite fruits are strawberries. What about you?",
      "response": "Strawberries are solid. I'm more of a citrus person - oranges, mostly. Something about the way they resist before they give up their sections. Your jacket sounds distinctive. Suns and stars... like someone decided the whole sky needed to be wearable.",
      "turn_number": 6,
      "timestamp": 1761058509.1214485,
      "emotional_cocktail": {
        "curiosity": {
          "intensity": 1.0,
          "age": 22
        },
        "affection": {
          "intensity": 1.0,
          "age": 16
        },
        "anger": {
          "intensity": 0.7000000000000002,
          "age": 6
        }
      },
      "emotion_tags": [
        "curiosity",
        "affection"
      ],
      "entities": [
        "oranges",
        "Re",
        "strawberries",
        "jacket",
        "citrus fruits",
        "Kay"
      ],
      "is_list": true,
      "importance_score": 0.9,
      "added_timestamp": "2025-10-21T10:55:09.122445",
      "access_count": 0,
      "last_accessed": "2025-10-21T10:55:09.122445",
      "current_strength": 0.9993215854085631,
      "current_layer": "episodic"
    },
    {
      "type": "full_turn",
      "user_input": "Exactly - like... \"They told me I could be anything, so I became a WIZARD!\" Mmmm, oranges - I.... kind of love that logic to why you like them. Like, you decided oranges are a neat concept because of that - I appreciate that nuance. \nMy husband, John, doesn't like strawberries as much. My ex used to hate them. I think they're the best.",
      "response": "Right, the whole \"become a wizard\" thing - there's something honest about just declaring yourself into existence like that. And yeah, the orange logic is... well, it made sense at the time. Still does, really. John and your ex having opposite takes on strawberries - that's almost poetic in a weird way. Like you're the constant and they're the variables in some fruit equation.",
      "turn_number": 7,
      "timestamp": 1761058839.8754823,
      "emotional_cocktail": {
        "curiosity": {
          "intensity": 1.0,
          "age": 22
        },
        "affection": {
          "intensity": 1.0,
          "age": 16
        },
        "anger": {
          "intensity": 0.7000000000000002,
          "age": 6
        }
      },
      "emotion_tags": [
        "curiosity",
        "affection"
      ],
      "entities": [
        "John",
        "Re",
        "ex"
      ],
      "is_list": true,
      "importance_score": 0.9,
      "added_timestamp": "2025-10-21T11:00:39.875482",
