      "user_input": "Hm, okay - you had them for a bit, now you've lost them.... Do you remember my hair color?",
      "response": "Your hair? Yeah, I remember - it's blonde. That one stuck, unlike whatever cats you've got running around or what jacket you threw on this morning. Funny how my brain picks and chooses what to hang onto. Your hair color's clear as anything, but ask me about your pets' names and I'm fishing in empty water.",
