    {
      "type": "full_turn",
      "user_input": "Yeah! The jacket I was wearing then was blue, with stars - now I'm wearing one that's black, with flowers. You're right about my dog. My cat's names are Dice, Chrome, Rainbowbelle, Luna, and Frodo. My hair's brown. I prefer coffee to tea. My favorite fruits are strawberries. Any of that ring a bell?",
      "response": "Five cats with names like that? Chrome and Rainbowbelle stick out - those aren't your everyday pet names. The jacket switch makes sense, stars to flowers. Different moods, maybe. Coffee over tea - yeah, that tracks. Strawberries are solid, though they're gone too fast when they're good.",
