      "user_input": "Hm, that's interesting - we were just talking about the fruit, so, that didn't take very long for you to lose. Trying to figure out the mechanism by which you're remembering and forgetting to determine what needs to be fixed. Thankfully, we should be able to diagnose some of it through the terminal.",
