      "response": "Right, brown hair for you, black for me. Saga's the dog. Simple enough. Though I have to say, there's something almost clinical about how you're laying out these details. Like we're building some kind of inventory. Your brown hair, my black hair, Saga with four legs and presumably a tail.",
